{"tid":1789701,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【有關本日有星火同盟手足被捕之跟進情況】","createTime":"2019-12-19T12:57:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-19T13:03:18.000Z","uid":91605,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f27eb732d969c11364ae1c2f5ad219e27baf2b43","tid":1789701,"uid":91605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T12:57:11.000Z","msg":"【有關本日有星火同盟手足被捕之跟進情況】<br />\n<br />\n有關是日 （二零一九年十二月十九日）警方對星火同盟手足的拘捕行動，由於本案已進入法律程序，星火同盟暫不便向外發佈更多資訊。所有被捕手足個案已有律師跟進。<br />\n<br />\n警方企圖以失實陳述，將本平台之運作扭曲成洗黑錢等惡意用途，意圖抹黑星火及其他支援頻道，本平台譴責此等抹黑行為。<br />\n<br />\n星火同盟在此感激各方的關心與支持。如有任何相關消息，我們將於本專頁公佈。<br />\n<br />\nsource: 星火Tg Channel"},{"pid":"8870c08cebca17077b1dc74f3eeb406c0fc004ee","tid":1789701,"uid":91605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T12:57:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"948fd382af21f9a6769a6e7a47efa61c59f9ba29","tid":1789701,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T12:57:33.000Z","msg":"Twitter戰線:要令星火事件上到國際！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1789690\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1789690</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">幫手入去將星火推到上國際</span>"},{"pid":"2f03d7927c46e3a38d585a912869108007df2a0a","tid":1789701,"uid":91605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T12:57:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"55bf088beebf38a59fa95ed70dca6d1b007c269e","tid":1789701,"uid":91605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T12:58:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ba9d31c5294c032fd078498ad86b4b838d55a02f","tid":1789701,"uid":91605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T12:58:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bcc7e6edc4c33440225dc708fb94e342fd1167b0","tid":1789701,"uid":91605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T12:58:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"241dec55ac46aabe5dacbf3486bbf56c6f060fe3","tid":1789701,"uid":91605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime